text: Rameshwar Phuyal (Nepali: रामेश्वर फुयाल) is a Nepalese politician, belonging to the CPN (Unified Marxist-Leninist). He is former member of Bagmati Provincial Assembly and former Minister for Physical Infrastructure and Development of Bagmati Province. == References == Category:Communist Party of Nepal (Unified Marxist–Leninist) politicians Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
